WEBVTT

00:17.000 --> 00:20.200
FLOWER-ADORNED GENERAL'S RESIDENCE

00:31.240 --> 00:32.800
Marquis, we're at the General's residence.

00:33.800 --> 00:35.120
-Changyu.
-What are you doing?

00:35.200 --> 00:36.360
I missed you.

00:36.960 --> 00:38.800
-Changyu…
-Do not do this.

00:38.880 --> 00:39.720
Calm down.

00:46.280 --> 00:47.400
The Marquis is gravely injured.

00:48.200 --> 00:49.560
You all stay here and keep watch.

00:49.640 --> 00:50.800
I will go fetch a physician.

00:52.680 --> 00:54.160
A doctor will not help with this.

00:55.600 --> 00:56.760
Why not?

01:04.360 --> 01:05.200
Why doesn't it work?

01:05.280 --> 01:06.520
You really don't understand?

01:11.200 --> 01:12.320
I see.

01:12.400 --> 01:14.440
I'll go to the Imperial Medical Office
to fetch a physician.

01:14.520 --> 01:15.440
Why bother?

01:15.520 --> 01:16.560
Right here…

01:17.400 --> 01:18.520
You would not get it anyway.

01:19.760 --> 01:22.120
You three, find a few reliable matrons.

01:22.200 --> 01:23.040
Post them at the corners,

01:23.120 --> 01:24.600
well out of sight. Let no one near.

01:24.680 --> 01:25.520
-Got it.
-Yes.

01:25.600 --> 01:26.480
Go on.

01:27.400 --> 01:28.240
What about me?

01:28.320 --> 01:29.920
Stop getting in the way. Come with me.

01:30.000 --> 01:30.840
Wait, but…

01:31.440 --> 01:33.760
You cannot spend your whole life
just fighting battles.

01:33.840 --> 01:35.440
You need to live some normal life.

01:36.120 --> 01:37.040
What part of life?

02:01.400 --> 02:02.480
Calm down first.

02:03.960 --> 02:05.120
I will go find a doctor.

02:38.920 --> 02:39.920
Who am I?

02:49.840 --> 02:51.000
Fan Changyu.

03:26.160 --> 03:28.080
It seems I will not be needed after all.

03:28.680 --> 03:29.560
That is even better.

03:29.640 --> 03:30.880
Let nature take its course.

03:31.400 --> 03:33.560
Sir, you haven't even checked on him--

03:34.600 --> 03:37.720
Are you the Imperial Physician or am I?

03:38.560 --> 03:39.400
I…

03:40.160 --> 03:42.600
I told you. This kind of thing
does not need a doctor.

03:42.680 --> 03:43.720
An imperial physician?

03:44.360 --> 03:45.440
What a wasted trip.

03:45.960 --> 03:46.920
Come on. Let's go.

03:48.800 --> 03:49.680
You two.

03:50.480 --> 03:51.440
Move along.

03:55.280 --> 03:57.320
Then what exactly
is this thing you call life?

05:30.560 --> 05:36.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:47.480 --> 05:49.520
The Emperor was slapped?

05:51.600 --> 05:54.080
Good. That fire I gifted him
was not wasted after all.

06:01.400 --> 06:02.600
A pity though.

06:02.680 --> 06:05.360
Marquis Wu'an and Fan Changyu
still managed to slip through.

06:06.400 --> 06:08.560
Your Li clan has a traitor within.

06:09.320 --> 06:10.720
You should deal with that properly.

06:11.560 --> 06:13.000
My grandson

06:13.520 --> 06:16.600
was briefly misled by Marquis Wu'an
and Fan Changyu

06:17.120 --> 06:19.120
and ruined today's plan.

06:20.160 --> 06:22.000
The fault lies with me.

06:23.680 --> 06:25.000
I will bear the blame.

06:25.760 --> 06:27.400
Grand Tutor, you are too modest.

06:27.480 --> 06:29.120
Still, this does achieve something.

06:30.720 --> 06:32.240
It has cut off any chance

06:32.320 --> 06:34.640
of Marquis Wu'an
joining forces with Qi Sheng.

06:35.240 --> 06:36.120
Besides,

06:36.640 --> 06:39.480
I have prepared a little gift
for that butcher girl.

06:40.080 --> 06:41.840
When Wei Yan hears of it,

06:42.360 --> 06:44.360
he will surely be pleased.

06:44.960 --> 06:46.240
And what gift would that be?

06:48.800 --> 06:51.600
The tiger tally he has been
so eager to obtain.

06:52.880 --> 06:54.480
The same tiger tally used

06:55.080 --> 06:57.160
to mobilize troops
in the northwest years ago?

06:58.960 --> 07:00.520
That is only the appetizer.

07:01.040 --> 07:02.760
The real feast is yet to come.

07:05.480 --> 07:06.640
-Please.
-Very well.

07:08.120 --> 07:08.960
Please.

07:57.520 --> 07:58.640
-Mother.
-I am here.

07:58.720 --> 08:00.800
Look how many osmanthus flowers I picked.

08:01.840 --> 08:03.080
Zheng, you did wonderfully.

08:03.160 --> 08:04.720
Later, let's use them

08:04.800 --> 08:06.800
to make some osmanthus candy, shall we?

08:06.880 --> 08:07.840
Great!

08:10.120 --> 08:11.040
Smell them.

08:37.480 --> 08:38.320
Mother.

08:42.679 --> 08:43.799
Zheng, you are here.

08:43.880 --> 08:45.480
Come sit. Have some osmanthus cakes.

09:05.960 --> 09:06.960
At last…

09:09.440 --> 09:10.600
I can see you again.

09:18.120 --> 09:19.400
You have someone by your side,

09:19.480 --> 09:22.200
someone who understands you
and will walk through life with you.

09:22.280 --> 09:23.880
I can finally rest easy.

09:28.760 --> 09:29.960
Just remember.

09:30.040 --> 09:31.560
My favorite treat

09:32.320 --> 09:34.200
has always been osmanthus cakes.

09:48.200 --> 09:49.120
What is wrong?

09:49.640 --> 09:50.920
Did you have a bad dream?

09:51.600 --> 09:52.600
It is nothing.

09:53.440 --> 09:55.560
Just some childhood memories.

10:13.240 --> 10:14.160
Changyu.

10:15.800 --> 10:17.560
You deserved more from me than this.

10:18.600 --> 10:20.480
I have failed you.

10:21.720 --> 10:23.120
When everything is settled,

10:23.640 --> 10:25.600
I will give you the wedding you deserve.

10:26.120 --> 10:27.840
You have not failed me.

10:29.240 --> 10:31.120
I chose to marry Xie Zheng.

10:31.200 --> 10:33.640
Yan Zheng married into my family.

10:34.560 --> 10:36.720
That was a fine wedding too.

10:38.800 --> 10:41.080
We never signed a divorce letter.

10:43.160 --> 10:44.440
So don't you deny it now.

10:47.440 --> 10:48.280
I won't.

10:49.800 --> 10:50.720
I married into your family.

10:52.040 --> 10:53.280
It is for life now.

11:00.560 --> 11:01.920
Ever since coming to the capital,

11:02.960 --> 11:05.480
trouble after trouble keeps appearing.

11:06.200 --> 11:08.680
Right now, all I want
is to clear my father's name,

11:09.200 --> 11:10.760
then return to Lin'an

11:11.360 --> 11:13.080
and live a simple, peaceful life.

11:15.400 --> 11:18.680
But after what happened last night,
I fear it will not be so simple.

11:21.160 --> 11:22.080
Do not worry.

11:22.760 --> 11:24.000
I already have a plan.

11:28.320 --> 11:30.000
GATHERING OF GRACE AND COMPASSION

11:54.000 --> 11:55.080
Slowly… Take it easy.

11:55.160 --> 11:56.040
Careful.

12:00.200 --> 12:03.200
I thought I would never see you again.

12:03.280 --> 12:06.160
I thought I would die there.

12:06.240 --> 12:07.200
It is all right.

12:07.280 --> 12:09.440
I am here now.

12:11.960 --> 12:13.080
Do not cry.

12:15.520 --> 12:16.360
There now.

12:28.240 --> 12:29.520
Last night…

12:31.720 --> 12:33.880
Did you stay here
and take care of me the whole night?

12:35.120 --> 12:36.240
Of course.

12:36.320 --> 12:38.560
You did not rest at all.

12:39.360 --> 12:40.560
How could you…

12:40.640 --> 12:43.840
Yesterday you rushed
into that fire to save me.

12:43.920 --> 12:45.880
I thought you might die in there.

12:45.960 --> 12:47.600
-Enough, enough.
-You must be hurt somewhere.

12:47.680 --> 12:49.480
-Let me see.
-That is enough.

12:49.560 --> 12:51.640
You are still weak. Do not talk so much.

12:53.400 --> 12:54.400
Listen to me.

12:59.520 --> 13:00.560
Before,

13:02.200 --> 13:03.920
I was always timid, always holding back.

13:05.480 --> 13:06.360
But this time,

13:07.000 --> 13:08.360
I want to tell you plainly.

13:08.440 --> 13:09.520
From now on,

13:10.800 --> 13:13.360
no matter what happens,
I will stay by your side.

13:13.440 --> 13:16.240
And the one who takes care of you
will be me. Only me.

13:43.520 --> 13:45.040
This tally does not match.

13:45.120 --> 13:46.040
It is fake.

13:47.760 --> 13:50.240
Your Highness, the tiger tally is genuine.

13:50.920 --> 13:53.240
Crown Prince Chengde and General Xie
cannot hold out much longer.

13:53.320 --> 13:55.160
Jinzhou is about to fall!

13:55.240 --> 13:58.080
For the sake of the realm and its people,

13:58.160 --> 14:00.520
please send reinforcements at once.

14:22.720 --> 14:23.760
General.

14:25.280 --> 14:26.120
Come in.

14:30.080 --> 14:31.120
What is it?

14:31.200 --> 14:32.040
General,

14:32.120 --> 14:34.320
Guard Jin has been waiting outside
for quite some time.

14:34.400 --> 14:36.280
He said once you wake,
you must go see him.

14:37.280 --> 14:38.320
I know.

14:38.400 --> 14:39.520
You may go.

14:43.200 --> 14:44.160
There is a letter here.

14:44.240 --> 14:45.480
You need to read it yourself.

14:53.480 --> 14:55.600
FAN CHANGYU, TO BE OPENED PERSONALLY

15:03.720 --> 15:06.080
I'VE SECURED THE FAKE TIGER TALLY…
PROOF TO CLEAR THE CASE…

15:06.160 --> 15:07.760
It is from Qian.

15:12.080 --> 15:13.120
SEALED

15:15.240 --> 15:16.080
The tiger tally!

15:17.120 --> 15:18.120
Where did this come from?

15:18.640 --> 15:20.680
Last night, a maid delivering a message

15:21.360 --> 15:23.120
collapsed and died right outside the gate.

15:25.280 --> 15:26.520
Help!

15:27.480 --> 15:30.680
FLOWER-ADORNED GENERAL'S RESIDENCE

15:31.720 --> 15:33.080
Help!

15:39.200 --> 15:40.360
Help!

15:43.280 --> 15:44.120
Someone come quickly!

15:55.120 --> 15:56.240
Dead?

15:59.200 --> 16:00.840
Take your weapons
and search the surroundings.

16:00.920 --> 16:02.680
See if there is anyone suspicious nearby.

16:02.760 --> 16:03.600
Yes!

16:09.160 --> 16:10.440
That dream just now…

16:11.280 --> 16:12.800
Could it be that somewhere in the heavens,

16:12.880 --> 16:15.120
even fate itself wants justice
for my father?

16:16.440 --> 16:17.280
General,

16:17.360 --> 16:19.000
someone called Shisan Niang
seeks an audience.

16:19.080 --> 16:20.280
Shisan Niang?

16:22.240 --> 16:23.400
I will go with you.

16:23.480 --> 16:24.480
No.

16:25.160 --> 16:26.840
I want to speak with her alone.

16:41.280 --> 16:44.440
Your wretched maid has already
delivered the tiger tally to Fan Changyu.

16:50.160 --> 16:52.120
-Deal with the body.
-Yes!

17:07.480 --> 17:08.640
So you weren't drunk that night?

17:15.200 --> 17:16.160
I love you so much.

17:16.240 --> 17:18.000
Why would you do this to me?

17:19.520 --> 17:20.839
Every time I start to believe

17:22.079 --> 17:23.760
you will not leave me,

17:23.839 --> 17:25.680
that you might stay by my side,

17:25.760 --> 17:27.880
this is always how it ends.

17:27.960 --> 17:29.760
Is my love worth so little to you

17:30.280 --> 17:31.400
that you would trample it?

17:31.480 --> 17:32.800
That is not love.

17:32.880 --> 17:34.960
That is possession! That is control!

17:38.160 --> 17:39.560
I will soon be the emperor.

17:40.160 --> 17:41.000
Without me,

17:41.520 --> 17:43.040
you will not be empress.

17:43.800 --> 17:44.880
You will be nothing.

17:45.480 --> 17:47.200
I have never cared about being empress.

17:47.800 --> 17:48.800
Without you,

17:49.880 --> 17:50.880
I would live far better.

17:59.920 --> 18:02.320
If you've got the guts, kill me.

18:17.760 --> 18:19.600
Are you hurt? Are you all right?

18:22.280 --> 18:23.640
I… I beg you.

18:24.240 --> 18:25.160
Just tell me.

18:25.840 --> 18:27.520
As long as you do not leave me,

18:28.080 --> 18:30.600
whatever you want, I will give it to you.

18:32.200 --> 18:34.040
I do not want anything from you.

18:36.360 --> 18:37.960
I only want to be free from you forever.

18:57.120 --> 18:58.240
You leave me no choice.

18:58.920 --> 19:00.800
-Bring the shackles.
-Yes!

19:13.200 --> 19:14.800
These were forged from hardened steel.

19:14.880 --> 19:16.080
No blade or axe can break them.

19:16.600 --> 19:17.560
If you try to run,

19:18.160 --> 19:20.600
one of us will lose a hand.

19:21.720 --> 19:22.920
You have gone mad.

19:23.640 --> 19:25.000
You truly have.

19:27.000 --> 19:27.920
You cannot escape.

19:29.480 --> 19:30.640
Not in this life.

19:31.160 --> 19:33.040
You belong to me alone.

19:53.040 --> 19:55.360
I never thought you'd still be alive.

19:59.600 --> 20:00.880
Why did you come to see me?

20:01.400 --> 20:02.640
To avenge Sui Yuanqing?

20:05.080 --> 20:06.280
Looks like

20:06.800 --> 20:09.320
I am the only one left
who still remembers to avenge him.

20:14.320 --> 20:15.520
Take this.

20:16.240 --> 20:17.600
Sui Yuanqing left it for you.

20:18.280 --> 20:19.200
And this as well.

20:24.120 --> 20:25.560
I will leave you a way to survive.

20:26.080 --> 20:28.280
Take this and go find Fan Changyu.

20:28.360 --> 20:31.920
A proper token from me
to prove your loyalty.

20:35.440 --> 20:36.680
The tiger tally is yours now.

20:37.400 --> 20:38.520
And he is dead.

20:39.960 --> 20:41.080
If I had to guess,

20:41.680 --> 20:44.960
he only wanted Qi Min
to fall into utter ruin.

20:45.040 --> 20:46.400
And you?

20:49.800 --> 20:50.800
What do you want?

20:53.800 --> 20:54.760
Me?

20:56.480 --> 20:58.240
Once, I thought you and Xie Zheng

20:59.240 --> 21:00.760
were my sworn enemies.

21:01.760 --> 21:03.040
You killed my brothers.

21:03.120 --> 21:04.920
Xie Zheng wiped out
my Qingfeng stronghold.

21:05.680 --> 21:07.040
Later, I believed

21:08.440 --> 21:10.200
Sui Yuanqing played with my feelings

21:10.280 --> 21:13.040
and dragged both me and the Qingfeng
stronghold into destruction.

21:13.840 --> 21:15.840
But today I finally see things clearly.

21:17.440 --> 21:20.160
Grudges in this world
are tangled in endless karma.

21:21.160 --> 21:22.760
Revenge has no end.

21:23.280 --> 21:24.720
If people keep killing each other,

21:25.240 --> 21:26.640
the killing will never stop.

21:28.400 --> 21:29.640
The tiger tally is yours now.

21:29.720 --> 21:31.720
-As for his…
-Take the head with you.

21:33.040 --> 21:34.320
I do not need it anymore.

21:34.840 --> 21:36.720
At least give him a whole body in death.

21:51.520 --> 21:52.960
Thank you for bringing this.

21:56.280 --> 21:58.160
I'll have a new travel pass
prepared for you.

21:58.800 --> 22:00.440
From this day on, you are free.

22:01.320 --> 22:02.480
Consider it my thanks

22:03.480 --> 22:04.800
for your kindness to Ning.

22:07.080 --> 22:08.680
But what's between us

22:09.960 --> 22:11.400
will be settled after I return.

22:16.320 --> 22:18.120
Then let us hope when we meet again,

22:18.640 --> 22:19.760
you are still alive.

22:30.360 --> 22:31.680
TIGER TALLY

22:36.760 --> 22:38.400
Qian sent this.

22:38.960 --> 22:41.000
Last night I dreamed of my father.

22:41.080 --> 22:42.880
When I woke,
this tiger tally was waiting for me.

22:43.760 --> 22:45.480
But I cannot understand it.

22:46.800 --> 22:49.000
Why would Prince Changxin frame my father?

22:49.600 --> 22:51.040
The defeat at Jinzhou,

22:52.720 --> 22:55.000
the deaths of hundreds of thousands
of soldiers…

22:56.880 --> 22:58.680
why was all of it
laid at my father's feet?

23:00.800 --> 23:03.960
My parents had lived under assumed names
for more than ten years.

23:05.320 --> 23:06.280
Why?

23:07.880 --> 23:09.640
Why were they still
hunted down and killed?

23:16.360 --> 23:19.120
I must prove
my father's innocence to the world.

23:21.720 --> 23:22.640
Your father

23:23.720 --> 23:25.840
and the soldiers who died unjustly
at Jinzhou

23:26.440 --> 23:28.000
all deserve the truth.

23:28.880 --> 23:30.280
But right now,

23:30.960 --> 23:32.840
this pair of tiger tallies alone

23:33.800 --> 23:36.840
cannot prove that Wei Yan
was the one behind it all.

23:38.520 --> 23:40.640
The mad palace maid who knew the truth

23:41.200 --> 23:43.040
already died in that fire.

23:43.560 --> 23:45.440
Nothing survived in Qingyuan Palace.

23:47.480 --> 23:49.920
Everyone tied to that matter

23:51.360 --> 23:52.960
has been silenced by Wei Yan.

23:53.680 --> 23:55.960
That mad maid once served Consort Qi.

23:57.600 --> 23:59.680
What connection did she have with Wei Yan?

24:01.800 --> 24:04.200
The palace rumors say
they were involved with each other.

24:04.960 --> 24:06.680
Then what truly happened back then?

24:06.760 --> 24:08.480
Is there really no clue left?

24:10.480 --> 24:11.760
What about Qi Sheng?

24:11.840 --> 24:13.480
Could he know something?

24:15.160 --> 24:16.240
Do not rush.

24:18.360 --> 24:19.920
Even if Qi Sheng knows anything,

24:20.000 --> 24:21.040
he would never dare say it.

24:22.240 --> 24:24.240
He has lived as a puppet for decades.

24:24.840 --> 24:26.920
Wei Yan terrifies him to the bone.

24:27.440 --> 24:28.840
He would never dare dig into the truth.

24:30.480 --> 24:32.000
Right now,

24:33.440 --> 24:34.920
if we want to bring down Wei Yan

24:35.000 --> 24:36.320
and make him answer for his crimes,

24:38.320 --> 24:39.560
we will have to use force.

24:41.440 --> 24:43.560
I have called him uncle
for more than 20 years.

24:43.640 --> 24:45.800
I know his nature well.

24:47.520 --> 24:48.520
I fear

24:49.960 --> 24:51.720
he has already begun to raise his troops.

24:56.320 --> 24:57.480
Do not worry.

24:58.560 --> 25:00.840
I will summon the full strength
of the Xie army.

25:01.720 --> 25:02.800
I will clear your father's name

25:03.640 --> 25:05.040
and give my father
the justice he deserves.

25:22.480 --> 25:25.840
So we have finally come to this.

25:30.320 --> 25:31.640
Very well.

25:32.640 --> 25:35.000
Then we move ahead of schedule.

25:36.040 --> 25:36.920
Send the order.

25:37.760 --> 25:39.960
Recall the troops to the capital at once.

25:40.040 --> 25:41.160
Yes!

25:43.200 --> 25:44.240
Hear the command!

25:44.320 --> 25:48.480
Spread word that Fan Changyu
is the daughter of the traitor Wei Qilin.

25:48.560 --> 25:50.560
-The faster the better.
-Yes!

26:11.200 --> 26:15.680
A LAND OF GRACE AND TALENT

26:35.040 --> 26:36.080
Flower-Adorned General,

26:36.160 --> 26:37.640
those who strike the Drum of Justice

26:37.720 --> 26:39.560
must first be paraded through the streets

26:39.640 --> 26:41.320
to face the people's accusations
and judgment

26:41.400 --> 26:42.560
before presenting their case.

26:48.200 --> 26:51.840
SPIRIT TABLET OF THE LATE LORD XIE LINSHAN
SPIRIT TABLET OF HIS WIFE, LADY WAN

26:51.920 --> 26:53.840
GUO'S TAVERN

27:00.680 --> 27:01.520
It is her!

27:01.600 --> 27:02.720
Everyone, come look!

27:02.800 --> 27:03.640
That is her!

27:03.720 --> 27:05.320
She is the traitor's daughter!

27:05.920 --> 27:07.520
-No one from the Wei clan is any good!
-Right!

27:07.600 --> 27:08.840
My father died in the Battle of Jinzhou!

27:08.920 --> 27:10.400
-Pay with your life!
-Nonsense!

27:10.480 --> 27:12.440
-Watch your mouth!
-Nonsense! Do you have any proof?

27:12.520 --> 27:14.400
Stop spreading lies! Changyu is innocent!

27:14.480 --> 27:15.560
SPIRIT TABLET OF THE LATE LORD XIE LINSHAN
SPIRIT TABLET OF HIS WIFE, LADY WAN

27:15.640 --> 27:16.640
Father.

27:17.320 --> 27:18.280
Mother.

27:19.320 --> 27:20.640
Your son has failed you.

27:21.960 --> 27:23.840
I beg that your spirits in heaven

27:24.920 --> 27:25.800
forgive me.

27:33.280 --> 27:34.560
-Hit her!
-Beat her to death!

27:34.640 --> 27:35.440
You menace!

27:35.520 --> 27:37.360
Say that again
and I'll rip your mouth apart!

27:37.440 --> 27:39.280
-You lost. Deal with it.
-Vengeance!

27:39.360 --> 27:40.520
Don't like it? Look away!

27:40.600 --> 27:42.560
The great traitor

27:42.640 --> 27:44.520
Wei Qilin

27:45.120 --> 27:47.280
Held the grain

27:47.360 --> 27:49.440
With no delivery

27:49.520 --> 27:53.480
Doomed a hundred thousand souls to end

27:54.520 --> 27:55.480
Hit her!

27:55.560 --> 27:56.800
Beat her to death!

27:56.880 --> 27:59.920
General Fan!

28:00.000 --> 28:01.640
Hit her!

28:01.720 --> 28:03.720
General Fan!

28:05.320 --> 28:07.080
General Fan!

28:07.160 --> 28:08.760
-Beat her to death!
-Beat her!

28:08.840 --> 28:11.160
General Fan!

28:11.240 --> 28:12.600
Hit her!

28:12.680 --> 28:13.720
Beat her to death!

28:13.800 --> 28:15.240
Hit her!

28:15.320 --> 28:16.560
Have you no shame?

28:16.640 --> 28:18.120
-Changyu.
-Changyu.

28:18.640 --> 28:19.480
Nonsense!

28:19.560 --> 28:20.840
How is she a general?

28:21.600 --> 28:22.480
Who threw that?

28:22.560 --> 28:23.480
-Who threw it?
-Who?

28:23.560 --> 28:24.560
-Good throw!
-Well done!

28:24.640 --> 28:26.200
-Nice throw!
-Are you people finished yet?

28:26.280 --> 28:27.880
-Resort to violence now?
-Stop!

28:32.920 --> 28:34.400
My father was Wei Qilin.

28:35.320 --> 28:36.680
But he was no traitor.

28:37.200 --> 28:38.440
He was framed!

28:38.520 --> 28:39.840
-He is your father!
-Your father killed them!

28:39.920 --> 28:41.160
Of course you say he is innocent.

28:41.240 --> 28:42.680
-Exactly!
-Hit her!

28:42.760 --> 28:44.200
-That enough yet?
-Hit her!

28:44.280 --> 28:45.200
All of you move aside!

28:45.280 --> 28:46.560
-Beat her to death!
-Right!

28:47.160 --> 28:48.240
Official business!

28:48.320 --> 28:49.760
-All bystanders step back!
-Move back!

28:50.560 --> 28:52.000
-Move back!
-Who does she think she is?

28:52.080 --> 28:53.680
-Move back!
-Are you hurt?

28:53.760 --> 28:55.000
Nonsense!

28:55.080 --> 28:56.200
Flower-Adorned General?

28:56.280 --> 28:57.560
More like a rebel general!

28:57.640 --> 28:58.560
Silence!

28:59.440 --> 29:01.280
Did any of you see it with your own eyes?

29:01.360 --> 29:03.680
Are you certain
that what you saw and heard

29:04.200 --> 29:05.680
is the real truth?

29:19.000 --> 29:19.920
I will go with you.

29:21.160 --> 29:22.320
-We will go with you.
-Me, too.

29:29.200 --> 29:31.280
You don't deserve living in this world!

29:31.360 --> 29:33.040
Get lost now!

29:49.800 --> 29:51.120
From here,

29:51.920 --> 29:52.920
I will go by myself.

29:57.440 --> 29:58.720
Once you take this step,

30:00.440 --> 30:01.960
there is no turning back.

30:04.840 --> 30:05.800
Let me do it.

30:11.880 --> 30:13.000
Let her do it.

30:30.880 --> 30:32.480
I am Fan Changyu of Qingping County.

30:32.560 --> 30:34.920
I lived at Xigu Alley
in the Town of Lin'an.

30:35.680 --> 30:36.840
I came today

30:37.480 --> 30:38.760
to petition the throne.

30:39.280 --> 30:40.200
Anyone who petitions the throne

30:40.280 --> 30:42.280
and speaks falsely is guilty
of deceiving the emperor.

30:42.360 --> 30:43.520
The punishment is death.

30:44.160 --> 30:45.440
Have you thought this through?

30:46.360 --> 30:47.600
I have.

30:49.000 --> 30:50.320
Today I bring three accusations.

30:50.400 --> 30:52.720
First, against Heaven's injustice.

30:53.920 --> 30:55.240
Wei Qilin!

30:55.320 --> 30:57.840
-You are nothing but a worse traitor!
-Criminal!

30:57.920 --> 30:58.960
-Traitor!
-Feed him to the dogs!

30:59.040 --> 31:00.920
-Let the dogs eat him!
-Hit her!

31:01.760 --> 31:04.360
Second, against an unwise ruler
who conceals the truth.

31:04.440 --> 31:06.200
GUARD YOUR THOUGHTS

31:06.280 --> 31:07.480
Who is beating the drum?

31:07.560 --> 31:08.640
Who dares beat the drum?

31:08.720 --> 31:09.720
Your Majesty,

31:09.800 --> 31:12.160
the Flower-Adorned General
has struck the Drum of Justice

31:12.240 --> 31:13.520
and seeks to petition the throne.

31:16.160 --> 31:17.480
Did Grand Tutor Li not say

31:17.560 --> 31:19.800
Xie Zheng and Fan Changyu
could be used to handle Wei Yan?

31:19.880 --> 31:20.960
Is this handling it?

31:21.040 --> 31:22.560
She beat the Drum of Justice!

31:25.960 --> 31:26.880
Third,

31:28.360 --> 31:30.400
against corrupt power holders.

31:33.400 --> 31:34.440
I, Fan Changyu,

31:34.960 --> 31:37.440
have come today to clear my father's name.

32:15.280 --> 32:16.200
Zheng.

32:17.520 --> 32:19.560
I made some osmanthus cakes for you.

32:20.680 --> 32:21.640
Zheng, just remember.

32:24.440 --> 32:26.160
My favorite treat has always been

32:26.240 --> 32:28.000
osmanthus cakes.

32:54.440 --> 32:57.280
To my Yan, when you read this,
imagine me before you.

32:57.360 --> 32:59.520
By the time you return victorious
and receive this letter,

32:59.600 --> 33:02.000
I will likely already be gone.

33:02.080 --> 33:03.520
If there is another life,

33:03.600 --> 33:05.200
may you live as a simple man,

33:05.280 --> 33:07.360
and I drift beside you in a humble boat.

33:07.440 --> 33:09.520
Rongyin's final words.

33:11.400 --> 33:12.880
So it was my brother heading back

33:12.960 --> 33:14.000
to the capital amid the war.

33:14.800 --> 33:16.640
It caused the fall of Jinzhou.

33:16.720 --> 33:17.960
SPIRIT TABLET OF THE LATE LORD XIE LINSHAN

33:18.040 --> 33:19.840
Which means Linshan's death

33:21.600 --> 33:24.240
was also caused by my brother's doing.

33:35.280 --> 33:36.200
Zheng,

33:36.720 --> 33:37.840
the world is in turmoil.

33:38.680 --> 33:40.920
The Xie family soldiers
are pressing your uncle

33:41.000 --> 33:44.040
to reveal the truth of Jinzhou.

33:45.040 --> 33:47.720
I am caught in the middle,
with no way out.

33:48.320 --> 33:52.080
Perhaps only my death
can quiet this conflict.

33:53.160 --> 33:56.280
Perhaps it will also awaken
your uncle's conscience

33:56.360 --> 33:58.080
and spare your life.

33:59.360 --> 34:00.320
Zheng,

34:00.840 --> 34:01.800
do not grieve for me.

34:03.320 --> 34:05.000
I will not be able to watch you grow up.

34:06.160 --> 34:07.120
Mother…

34:07.840 --> 34:09.320
I have failed you.

34:10.760 --> 34:13.760
Only now do I understand the sacrifice
you made and the meaning behind it.

34:43.880 --> 34:45.320
WEI RESIDENCE

34:45.400 --> 34:46.120
WEI RESIDENCE

34:46.199 --> 34:47.320
Stop it!

34:47.400 --> 34:48.880
Stop beating that drum!

34:50.679 --> 34:53.159
Her Highness the Grand Princess arrives!

34:53.760 --> 34:55.040
Brother.

34:58.960 --> 35:00.440
-Your Majesty!
-Sister.

35:00.960 --> 35:02.200
I know what you came to say.

35:02.280 --> 35:04.480
But now is not the time
for your friendship.

35:04.560 --> 35:06.440
Once the Drum of Justice is struck,

35:06.520 --> 35:09.320
the emperor must hold court
and hear the grievances of the people.

35:09.400 --> 35:12.080
Her case has been twisted and spread
by those with their own schemes.

35:12.160 --> 35:13.480
The whole realm now knows of it.

35:13.560 --> 35:15.440
Brother, you cannot avoid this.

35:18.160 --> 35:19.120
Brother.

35:20.520 --> 35:22.400
You set a trap for Xie Zheng

35:23.280 --> 35:25.240
and nearly cost my life.

35:26.000 --> 35:28.040
I have yet to settle that account.

35:28.560 --> 35:31.680
But if you show
the authority of an emperor

35:31.760 --> 35:33.760
and clear Changyu's name,

35:34.760 --> 35:36.040
I will let the matter rest.

35:41.160 --> 35:42.120
Brother,

35:42.200 --> 35:43.440
respect yourself, or others won't.

35:43.520 --> 35:45.240
Carry yourself like an emperor.

35:45.320 --> 35:47.160
Will you truly spend your life
as a puppet?

35:57.720 --> 35:58.680
Guards.

36:01.200 --> 36:02.640
Summon Fan Changyu

36:03.400 --> 36:04.480
to the Hall of Exalted Virtue.

36:06.480 --> 36:08.040
Time for me to act like an emperor.

36:21.720 --> 36:23.680
HALL OF EXALTED VIRTUE

36:23.760 --> 36:25.600
Wei Qilin was framed

36:25.680 --> 36:27.800
in the Jinzhou case 17 years ago.

36:28.800 --> 36:31.240
Today I, Fan Changyu,
am willing to stake my life

36:31.760 --> 36:34.760
to beg Your Majesty to uphold justice

36:36.800 --> 36:38.400
and set the truth right.

36:47.680 --> 36:51.520
This is the tiger tally Wei Qilin carried
to Chongzhou to request reinforcements.

36:52.640 --> 36:53.680
This is the truth.

36:54.920 --> 36:56.280
Yet back then,

36:56.360 --> 36:58.880
Prince Changxin claimed
this tally was forged

36:58.960 --> 37:00.040
and refused to send troops.

37:00.560 --> 37:02.320
That delay led to the disaster at Jinzhou.

37:02.920 --> 37:03.840
It proves

37:03.920 --> 37:05.960
someone deliberately
sabotaged the operation.

37:06.040 --> 37:07.640
The Xie and Wei families

37:08.160 --> 37:09.400
were both victims to the plot.

37:14.600 --> 37:16.000
If your claim proves true,

37:16.840 --> 37:17.840
Minister Fan,

37:18.520 --> 37:20.000
what punishment do you seek?

37:21.480 --> 37:22.680
That object is a forgery.

37:24.600 --> 37:26.440
What shameless nonsense.

37:27.480 --> 37:28.840
What makes you say it's fake?

37:29.440 --> 37:30.760
Why, you ask?

37:31.400 --> 37:33.560
Because among everyone here,

37:33.640 --> 37:36.240
the only person present
when that tragedy unfolded

37:36.320 --> 37:37.800
was me.

37:38.760 --> 37:40.640
You claim that object is real.

37:41.200 --> 37:42.600
Then where is your proof?

37:43.800 --> 37:46.280
Though I have only recently
taken command on the battlefield,

37:46.800 --> 37:47.920
even I know

37:48.520 --> 37:50.400
that every tiger tally
is recorded in the archives

37:50.920 --> 37:52.120
with official seals.

37:52.200 --> 37:53.480
It can be verified.

37:54.720 --> 37:58.600
All those records were destroyed
in the great fire 17 years ago.

38:01.160 --> 38:02.400
What a convenient coincidence.

38:03.160 --> 38:05.200
Coincidence or not, that is the truth.

38:05.840 --> 38:07.520
And I know very well

38:07.600 --> 38:09.680
why you cling so stubbornly
to this matter.

38:09.760 --> 38:11.000
In the end,

38:11.080 --> 38:13.800
it is nothing more
than your own selfish obsession.

38:17.520 --> 38:19.480
TO THE CHANCELLOR

38:22.480 --> 38:23.720
This is

38:23.800 --> 38:26.600
a letter written
by General He Jingyuan himself.

38:26.680 --> 38:30.720
It exposes this woman's true identity.

38:32.480 --> 38:34.440
Your Majesty, please have a look.

38:37.240 --> 38:39.880
Back then, Wei Qilin fled the battlefield

38:39.960 --> 38:41.320
and died a disgraceful death.

38:41.840 --> 38:44.080
The only one who slipped through the net

38:45.400 --> 38:46.680
was you.

38:46.760 --> 38:49.800
Wei Qilin's daughter, Wei Changyu.

38:50.720 --> 38:51.840
Wei Yan!

38:53.360 --> 38:55.280
Stop twisting the truth.

38:55.800 --> 38:57.440
I, Fan Changyu, stand here
with a clear conscience.

38:57.520 --> 38:58.880
Wei Changyu,

38:58.960 --> 39:01.520
you escaped punishment back then.

39:01.600 --> 39:03.920
And today you dare stand
in this imperial court,

39:04.000 --> 39:06.640
spreading lies and trying
to throw Dayin into chaos.

39:06.720 --> 39:08.600
Such treason deserves death.

39:08.680 --> 39:09.520
Your Majesty,

39:09.600 --> 39:13.000
today I impeach this remnant
of the Wei family.

39:13.080 --> 39:13.920
She should be executed

39:14.000 --> 39:15.280
to appease the spirits

39:15.360 --> 39:18.240
of the hundred thousand soldiers
who died at Jinzhou.

39:18.320 --> 39:19.920
And who exactly is the real remnant here?

39:21.200 --> 39:22.240
Your Majesty,

39:22.320 --> 39:23.560
ministers,

39:27.160 --> 39:28.880
if my father truly were a villain,

39:28.960 --> 39:31.120
then why would General He Jingyuan,
a trusted confidant of Wei Yan…

39:31.200 --> 39:32.040
DILIGENT IN RULE, DEVOTED TO THE WORTHY

39:32.120 --> 39:33.960
…have corresponded with him and insisted

39:34.040 --> 39:35.560
on protecting my sister and me?

39:38.120 --> 39:39.880
I have a question for Chancellor Wei.

39:40.480 --> 39:43.520
Behind my father's wrongful persecution,

39:44.040 --> 39:46.080
who gained the most from it?

39:46.160 --> 39:47.360
Who benefits?

39:49.000 --> 39:50.680
General Fan speaks the truth.

39:55.800 --> 39:57.040
I too would like to ask

39:57.560 --> 40:00.600
who benefited the most
from that case all those years ago.

40:05.560 --> 40:07.040
I heard that Your Majesty intends

40:07.560 --> 40:09.960
to reopen the tragic Jinzhou case
17 years ago.

40:11.120 --> 40:13.480
That case concerns my father Xie Linshan,

40:13.560 --> 40:14.840
the late Crown Prince Chengde,

40:14.920 --> 40:16.040
and the hundred thousand fallen soldiers.

40:16.120 --> 40:17.880
If the case is to be reopened,

40:18.560 --> 40:21.080
how could I possibly remain absent?

40:21.760 --> 40:23.200
The nation's enemy remains unpunished.

40:23.280 --> 40:24.960
Your family's vengeance
is still unresolved.

40:25.040 --> 40:26.120
Yet today,

40:26.920 --> 40:30.320
you come here to defend
the daughter of a traitor.

40:30.400 --> 40:32.200
The palace fire isn't settled yet,

40:32.280 --> 40:34.520
and you are already speaking for her.

40:35.360 --> 40:38.320
Could it be that you too
harbor treasonous intentions?

40:41.080 --> 40:43.000
If anyone here harbors treason,

40:43.080 --> 40:45.120
I fear it is someone else.

40:53.800 --> 40:54.800
This letter

40:55.720 --> 40:58.880
was written by Consort Qi
to Wei Yan, pleading for help.

40:59.520 --> 41:01.160
Because of a private affair,

41:01.680 --> 41:03.240
Wei Yan returned to the capital midway,

41:03.840 --> 41:05.960
leaving the soldiers of Jinzhou
to face the enemy alone.

41:06.480 --> 41:08.520
In the end, it led directly
to that great catastrophe.

41:16.200 --> 41:18.160
…I KNOW YOU ARE TRAPPED IN JINZHOU…
THE CONSPIRATORS' SCHEME RUNS DEEP…

41:18.240 --> 41:20.240
FATHER AND BROTHER ARE TRAPPED, YET I AM
CONFINED IN THE PALACE. I BEG YOUR AID…

41:22.200 --> 41:23.800
A thief crying thief.

41:24.800 --> 41:25.640
Wei Yan,

41:26.160 --> 41:29.160
you are the true traitor
behind the disaster at Jinzhou!

41:29.680 --> 41:32.360
HALL OF THE SUPREME ULTIMATE

41:43.480 --> 41:46.040
DAYIN

41:46.120 --> 41:48.400
There are men loyal to us
within the Imperial Guard.

41:48.480 --> 41:51.280
The palace gates will fall
without a fight.

41:52.240 --> 41:55.360
I have already spread word
through the Bureau of Astronomy.

41:55.880 --> 41:58.080
These years of drought and flood
are said to be caused

41:58.600 --> 42:00.680
by the disruption of the dragon veins,

42:00.760 --> 42:02.640
the result of an illegitimate succession.

42:03.440 --> 42:06.160
Your Highness is the descendant
of Crown Prince Chengde.

42:06.240 --> 42:09.560
Your ascension is what the people desire

42:09.640 --> 42:11.120
and what the court expects.

42:12.800 --> 42:13.680
Good.

42:14.320 --> 42:15.880
Seventeen years.

42:16.400 --> 42:19.200
At last, I have returned to this place.

44:57.720 --> 45:00.720
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

45:00.800 --> 45:01.680
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
